
## POWER OUTSIDE MIRROR REMOVAL/INSTALLATION  


1. Disconnect the negative battery cable. 
2. Remove the door speaker. (Refer to 09-20 DOOR SPEAKER REMOVAL/INSTALLATION.) 
3. Disconnect the power outside mirror connector. 
4. Turn the power outside mirror forward. 
5. Remove the screws. 
6. Remove the power outside mirror.  


4. If not as specified, replace the power outside mirror.  


7. Install in the reverse order of removal.  

